   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#FNAnker_148_148" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">[148]</text:span></text:a> ankh. Br. 8, 3 (Deussen).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#FNAnker_149_149" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">[149]</text:span></text:a> Vaj. Samh. 23, 48 (Deussen).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#FNAnker_150_150" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">[150]</text:span></text:a> atap. Br. 8, 5, 3, 7 (Deussen).</text:p>
