   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#FNAnker_152_152" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">[152]</text:span></text:a> Atharvaveda. 2, l. 4, l. II, 5.</text:p>
